Office of Accountant General of the Federation on fire
SaharaReporters Media


Treasury House where the office of Nigeria’s Accountant General is located in the Federal Capital Territory, Abuja, is currently on fire. It was gathered that the fire started from the third floor and razed most parts of the building upwards including the floor where the Accountant General’s office is situated. Firefighters are currently battling to put out the fire. More to come…